title: BRIEF-Fortnox Q3 operating profit up at SEK 7.8 million
text:
BRIEF-Fortnox Q3 operating profit up at SEK 7.8 million 
Oct 21 Fortnox AB : 
* Q3 operating profit 7.8 million Swedish crowns ($940,540.93) versus 6.3 million crowns year ago 
* Q3 net sales 32.2 million crowns versus 23.7 million crowns year ago 
* End-Q3 order backlog at 112 million crowns
